# nodaf
## (Cym)

mae `nodaf` yn raglen siml am nodu syniadau. Mae mor syml Ã¢ hynny. Mae'r
llinell cyntaf yw'r teitl, y gweddill yw'r corff.

Cyn rhedeg `nodaf` wnewch siwr bod `$XDG_DATA_HOME` wedi osod. Bydd `nodaf`
yn creu `$XDG_DATA_HOME/nodaf` iddwch.
I creu nodyn ```
[llwybr nodaf] newidd [enw nodyn]
```
I darllen nodyn ```
[llwybr nodaf] gafael [enw nodyn]
```


## (Eng) I note

`nodaf` is a simple program for noting down ideas. That's it.
the first line is the title, the rest is the body.

Before running `nodaf` make sure that you have `$XDG_DATA_HOME` set. `nodaf`
will create `$XDG_DATA_HOME/nodaf` for you.
To create a note ```
[path to nodaf] new [note name]
```
To read a note ```
[path to nodaf] get [note name]
```
